## 4. Non-functional requirements
- NFR1. Time-to-running on a fresh box: < 30 min via bootstrap.
- NFR2. No secrets in git; secret scan in CI must pass.
- NFR3. All agent actions reconstructable from audit log alone.
- NFR4. Memory + embeddings stay local (no external embedding calls).
- NFR5. Runtime swap (Hermes -> other) requires changing only `agent/runtime.config.yaml` + `mcp/` configs, not skills/brain.
- NFR6. Every skill has at least one passing eval fixture in CI.

