## 8. Reliability metrics to track (from first skill live)
- M1. First-pass acceptance rate (drafts merged without substantive edits). Target > 70% within 4 weeks/skill.
- M2. Mean time to detect agent error. Target < 24h.
- M3. Verifier pass rate on first attempt per skill.

