## 9. Definition of Done (MVP)
- DoD1. Fresh-box clone + bootstrap -> running agent in < 30 min.
- DoD2. meeting-synth, ticket-draft, policy-redline, csf-crosswalk, daily-brief all pass golden-fixture evals in CI.
- DoD3. All A3+ actions blocked without an approved CPO; audit log reconstructs every action.
- DoD4. No secrets in git; secret scan + redaction tests pass.
- DoD5. GRC + ticket adapters present but disabled; file-only mode fully functional.
- DoD6. Public template + private-fork instructions documented.

